Class JsonCraftingAttributeReader

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.inventory.fileReader.CraftingAttributeReader
de.oth.blocklib.inventory.fileReader.JsonCraftingAttributeReader
public class JsonCraftingAttributeReader
extends CraftingAttributeReader
Reads information about recipes from json-meta-files Uses the MetaInfoManager to read the files and extracts the info from there
